<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL33">
<l>meyyellām pōka viṭṭu virikuḻa lāriṟ paṭṭup</l>
<l>poyyelām potintu koṇṭa pōṭkaṉēṉ vantu niṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>aiyaṉē yaraṅka ṉēyuṉ ṉaruḷeṉṉu mācai taṉṉāṟ</l>
<l>poyyaṉēṉ vantu niṉṟēṉ poyyaṉēṉ poyya ṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Lord! I, a deceiver,</l>
<l rend="indent">who let go of all truths, got entrapped in women with loose hair [and]</l>
<l rend="indent">stored up all falsehoods,</l>
<l>have come and stood [here].</l>
<l>O Raṅga[nātha]! O [You] from Raṅgam!</l>
<l>I, a liar, have come and stood [here]</l>
<l>Out of desire for Your grace,</l>
<l>I, a liar, am a liar!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
